\v 20 Nipakuo a w…îy…õ Israel atuk…îfo…î
\q2 b…õfa Kanaan asase no ak…îsi Sarefat;
\q1 na atuk…îfo…î a w…îfiri Yerusalem a
\q2 w…îte Safarad no b…õfa Negeb nkuro no adi so.
